  {
    "model": "resources.psychoarticle",
    "pk": 1,
    "fields": {
      "title": "當壓力滿出來時，先做這 3 件事",
      "category": "壓力管理",
      "read_minutes": 4,
      "excerpt": "壓力不是敵人，它是身體在提醒你「需要被照顧了」。學會辨識身體訊號，用呼吸與書寫幫自己降載。",
      "content_markdown": "",
      "is_active": true,
      "created_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
    }
  },
  {
    "model": "resources.psychoarticle",
    "pk": 2,
    "fields": {
      "title": "情緒沒有好壞，只有需要被聽見",
      "category": "情緒覺察",
      "read_minutes": 5,
      "excerpt": "我們常急著趕走難過。其實每個情緒都帶著訊息，練習「命名情緒」，是與自己和解的第一步。",
      "content_markdown": "",
      "is_active": true,
      "created_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
    }
  },
  {
    "model": "resources.psychoarticle",
    "pk": 3,
    "fields": {
      "title": "與焦慮共處：把「萬一」變成「就算」",
      "category": "焦慮",
      "read_minutes": 6,
      "excerpt": "焦慮愛問「萬一⋯⋯怎麼辦」。試著改成「就算發生了，我可以⋯⋯」，把失控感轉回掌控感。",
      "content_markdown": "",
      "is_active": true,
      "created_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
    }
  },
  {
    "model": "resources.psychoarticle",
    "pk": 4,
    "fields": {
      "title": "睡不著的夜晚，先別逼自己睡著",
      "category": "睡眠",
      "read_minutes": 4,
      "excerpt": "越逼自己入睡越清醒。建立溫柔的睡前儀式，讓身體知道：現在很安全，可以放鬆了。",
      "content_markdown": "",
      "is_active": true,
      "created_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
    }
  },
  {
    "model": "resources.psychoarticle",
    "pk": 5,
    "fields": {
      "title": "照顧自己，從一杯水一次深呼吸開始",
      "category": "自我照顧",
      "read_minutes": 3,
      "excerpt": "自我照顧不必很盛大。微小而持續的善待，會慢慢長成心裡的韌性。",
      "content_markdown": "",
      "is_active": true,
      "created_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
    }
  },
  {
    "model": "resources.psychoarticle",
    "pk": 6,
    "fields": {
      "title": "設立界線，不是拒絕愛，而是保護愛",
      "category": "人際關係",
      "read_minutes": 5,
      "excerpt": "說「不」會內疚嗎？界線讓關係更長久。練習溫柔而堅定地表達自己的需要。",
      "content_markdown": "",
      "is_active": true,
      "created_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
    }
  },
